					<h3 class="article__content-title">Embarking on a yoga journey. A beginner's guide</h3>

					<div class="article__content-text">
						<p>Let's explore how proper breathing can be the key to physical and emotional well-being. This article on
							pranayama will provide clear techniques and practical tips to help breathing become your reliable guide in
							the world of yoga.</p>
						<p>Breathing is not just a physiological process that supplies oxygen to the body and removes carbon
							dioxide. In the world of yoga, breathing plays a key role in the process of healing and achieving harmony
							between body and mind. The principles of breathing in yoga are studied and developed using a practice
							known as pranayama.</p>
						<p>Pranayama is an ancient practice of breath control that has its roots in the Vedic tradition. “Prana” in
							Sanskrit means life energy, and “ayama” means control. Thus, pranayama refers to the control of life
							energy through breathing.</p>
