					</div>

					<div class="article__content-tip">
						Before beginning pranayama practice, it is important to consult with an experienced yoga instructor.
						Uncontrolled breathing exercises can have undesirable consequences. Systematic and regular practice of
						pranayama, combined with other aspects of yoga, can lead to improved physical and mental health, helping to
						achieve harmony and balance in life.
